Give me a sign ♪</i>

54
00:03:40,361 --> 00:03:43,277
<i>♪ Put down your lies ♪</i>

55
00:03:45,986 --> 00:03:48,819
<i>♪ Lay down next to me ♪</i>

56
00:03:49,069 --> 00:03:51,485
<i>♪ Don't listen when I scream ♪</i>

57
